bilingual.source: I have managed to keep my presence aboard Endeavour secret.
bilingual.target: 我成功地在奋进号上保密了我的存在。
她的存在点亮了我的一天。
他故意忽视了她的存在。

bilingual.source: She felt a strange presence anear her.
bilingual.target: 她感觉到有一种奇怪的存在靠近她。

bilingual.source: The water turned green due to algal presence.
bilingual.target: 由于藻类的存在，水变绿了。

bilingual.source: The presence of exudate indicates an infection.
bilingual.target: 渗出物的存在表明有感染。

bilingual.source: He sensed her presence before he saw her.
bilingual.target: 他在看到她之前就感觉到她的存在。

bilingual.source: The presence of mold can taint the air quality.
bilingual.target: 霉菌的存在会污染空气质量。
官僚主义的存在让人们感到沮丧。

bilingual.source: She felt a drack presence in the old house.
bilingual.target: 她在老房子里感受到一种黑暗的存在。

list.abstract: 莅临是一个汉语词语，读音是lì lín，意思是指，来到；来临，光临。出自于（清）黄轩祖 《游梁琐记·王天冲》：“某早闻之，不敢莅临，遣其弟代祭。”

yingyinNormal.en: You don't see who's controlling who. Within that man made prototype I fought, I sensed the presence of Megatron.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们不晓得是谁在控制谁，我和那个人造变形金刚战斗时，可以感觉到威振天的存在。

yingyinNormal.en: I have ample protection. I welcome your presence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的防御固若金汤，但我仍欢迎你的到来。

yingyinNormal.en: Acknowledging presence of genetic material. Analyzing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 正在确认基因物质。正在分析。

yingyinNormal.en: Her presence undermines my authority as Secretary of State.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她的在场会削弱我作为国务卿的权威。

yingyinNormal.en: So we are currently in the presence of Leonard Nimoy's DNA.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在在大家面前的是伦纳德·尼莫伊的DNA。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, Mitch, I'm liking the new hat. It gives you some presence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 米奇尔，我喜欢这顶新帽子，让你看起来不一样了。

yingyinNormal.en: But if we don't establish a presence in the region, it's gonna be too late.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但如果我们不在当地立足，那就太迟了。

yingyinNormal.en: Every form he's built, every trace of his presence on the net. We have to act now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他制造的机器，他在网络上的一切痕迹，我们必须马上行动。

yingyinNormal.en: I am Sendi, your chamber presence. New clothes? We wish only to attend your needs.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是Sendi，您的专属侍者。新衣服？希望能满足您的需求。

yingyinNormal.en: Seth! Witnesses report an FBI and Homeland presence at the Knoxville voting center.
yingyinNormal.zh: 赛斯！有目击者称，诺克斯维尔投票中心出现了联调局和国安局的人。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, which means they'll lose face and compensate by increasing their ground presence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那他们就会丢面子，进而增加派军来挽回这个面子。

yingyinNormal.en: He's not getting off. By reason of insanity. Don't question my client outside my presence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他不能逃脱罪名。由于精神错乱的缘故，别在我不在场的时候盘问我当事人。

yingyinNormal.en: The Emperor is breathing his last and he has requested the presence of his imperial consort.
yingyinNormal.zh: 皇上只剩最后一口气了，他要求见他的皇后。

yingyinNormal.en: I've identified the host as general Zod of Kandor. Acknowledging presence of foreign genetic material. Analyzing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 已辨认出基因主人为坎多城的佐德将军。正在确认外来基因物质。正在分析。

yingyinNormal.en: Very well. Enjoy yourself. You're going to be in the presence of something that I've dreamed of seeing for decades.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，玩得开心。你将亲眼目睹我所梦寐以求了十多年的伟大成就。

yingyinNormal.en: I've had ample opportunity to observe Browning and adopt his physical presence, study his mannerisms, and so on and so forth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经观察多日，习惯他的外貌特征 行为举止等。

yingyinNormal.en: Your previous employer, here, says you are a warm, chatty and life-enhancing presence with a lot of potential. Yes, I paid him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的上任雇主说你是一个热心，健谈，让人难忘，拥有无限潜力的人。对，我贿赂他让他这么说的。

yingyinNormal.en: I've known them separately and I've known them together and to know them as a couple is to know that you are truly in the presence of love.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看过他们单身跟交往时的样子，我知道他们交往时深爱着彼此。

yingyinNormal.en: It was said that the gods fashioned her eyes out of the stars and that roses were ashamed to bloom in the presence of her ruby lips. Oh, my.
yingyinNormal.zh: 传说，她的眼睛是神用星星做的，她艳红的唇，令玫瑰都羞于开放。我的天。

yingyinNormal.en: They basically want to tell us that whatever we learned from Dunkin' Donuts, whatever historical presence for price was, was now irrelevant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们想透露的是我们所知道的邓肯甜甜圈的价格以及过去物品的价格都与他们毫无关系。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The ruling is a victory for big chains with a <highlight>presence</highlight> in many states, since they usually collect sales tax on online purchases already.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 裁决对那些在许多地方都有实体存在的大公司而言是件幸事，因为他们在网上已经缴完税了。

examination_example.sentence: Each year the physical <highlight>presence</highlight> rule becomes further removed from economic reality and results in significant revenue losses to the States.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每年，实体存在规则都进一步脱离经济现实，给美国带来巨大的收入损失。

examination_example.sentence: A business was shipping a customer's purchase to a state where the business didn't have a physical <highlight>presence</highlight> such as a warehouse or office.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一家公司将客户购买的商品运送到一个该公司没有实体--如仓库或办公室--存在的州。
